data.description: Country living away from the hustle-bustle of work.  You will feel like you are on a relaxing vacation! The covered deck offers a comfortable space for outdoor activities & relaxation, even during inclement weather. The 3.19-acre lot provides ample room for outdoor activities & privacy in a serene setting. The open great room concept creates a spacious & inviting living area, combining the living rm, dining area, & kitchen into one cohesive space. The split bedroom concept separates the master suite from the other bedrooms for added privacy.  The walkout basement offers an additional family room, bedroom, & bath, as well as a much desired large John Deere room with a large shop area. This wonderful home is conveniently located just minutes away from downtown Cape  allowing easy access to shopping, dining, & entertainment options in the city. Moreover, its proximity to the National Trail of Tears Park makes it an attractive location for nature enthusiasts, hikers, and history lovers.
